# Siemens PLC Maintenance Guide

## PLC Communication Timeout

Alarm Code:
PLC-COM-502

Description

Communication between CPU and remote I/O modules has timed out.

Troubleshooting

Step 1
Check Ethernet cable.

Step 2
Verify switch LEDs.

Step 3
Ping remote PLC.

Step 4
Restart communication module.

Acceptable Ping Latency

<2 ms

Recommended Firmware

v3.8.12
